  <brief_title>Evaluation of Bone Union Following Anterior Cervical Fusion Using a NovoMax™</brief_title>
  <official_title>Evaluation of Bone Union Following Anterior Cervical Fusion Using a Bioactive Glass-Ceramic Spacer (NovoMax™): Comparison With a PEEK Cage Filled With β-Tricalcium Phosphate (Cervios ChronOs™)</official_title>
