  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the efficacy and safety of NovoMax™ in Anterior
      Cervical Interbody Fusion - Comparison of NovoMax™ versus ChronOs®.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
